Your task is to jump over obstacles, collect coins, and avoid enemies to achieve the highest score possible. JoJo Jump has beautiful graphics and lively sound, bringing players a great entertainment experience. This extension is easy to install and can be played directly on the Chrome browser without downloading or installing any other software. Download JoJo Jump today to experience the excitement and thrill of this game!

HOW TO PLAY 
press right arrow to move right, press left arrow to move left,try not to fall and try not collision with the enemy
